<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>183</hymn_number>
<title>BAWIPA, NA PENNAK KA DUH CH183</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawipa nangmah pennak, Keimah nih ka duh ko, Kan tlanhtu nih a thi
 sung in, A khamhmi Khrihfabu.

[V2]
 Pathian, na Khrihfabu, Na hmaiah an dir ko, Nang ca a sung bikmi an
 si, Na kut chung an um ko.

[V3]
 Pathian na pennak ca'h, Ka thlacamnak a kai, Ka thazang lungtho in ka
 pek, Vawlei rian a dih tiang.

[V4]
 Lawmhnak sung bik nakin, Van lam ka sunter deuh, Hawikomhnak thiang
 biakam sung le, A dawt thangthatnak hla.

[V5]
 Na biatak a hmunh bang, Vawlei sunparnak le, Vancung lunglawmhnak sung
 bik cu, Zion nih a co lai.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
</song>